            "title": "日股高收1163點或2.33% 重越51000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股午後愈戰愈勇，非但升穿51000點，且以全日高位收市，成交做出三連升的成績。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經平均指數收報51028點，漲1163點或2.33%；過去3日累計共升3.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479958-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61163%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%962-33-%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a51000%e9%bb%9e",
